Package: macdown
Title: An updated R Markdown thesis template using the bookdown package
Version: 0.1.4-1
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Antonio",
           family = "PÃ¡ez",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "paezha@mcmaster.ca",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6912-9919"))
Description: This is a modified version of the 'thesisdown' package. It uses the 
    bookdown package and LaTeX graduate thesis templates from McMaster University, 
    this package aims to encourage reproducible research using simple Markdown 
    syntax while embedding all of the 'R' code to produce plots and analyses as well.
Maintainer: Antonio Paez <paezha@mcmaster.ca>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0)
Suggests:
    remotes,
    usethis
